brokerageName: Campion & Company Fine Homes Real Estate
description: Welcome to #12 at the Trolley House, a 24-unit building located on a quiet street close to all the best restaurants & entertainment the neighborhood has to offer as well as easy access to the beach, major highways, Seaport, South End & more. A fantastic 2 bedroom condo w/ expansive living space, large eat-in kitchen & ample room for dining, entertaining, & working, not to mention 2 full baths, 2 garage parking & a courtyard for lounging! The home features a large coat closet & foyer w/ space for side tables, benches & books. Make your way to the living area w/ a generous kitchen featuring plentiful cabinets, cooking space, island seating & updated appliances. Lavishly scaled, the fireplaced living area is a delight & is reminiscent of the suburbs with room to do it all. Windows on all sides, sunlight pours in throughout the day. Primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom, second bedroom has a dedicated bathroom & works well as a guest room/office. Lots of closets & extra garage storage.
